---
import "../../../public/css/commercialHp/commercialHp1.css";
---

<section id="commercialHpIntro" class="cmhp-section">
    <div class="cmhp-intro__content">
        <div class="cmhp-intro__title parallax" data-depth="3">
            <div class="cmhp-heading lg parallax split--char">
                커머셜 홈페이지, <div class="color-or">왜 </div> 지금 필요한가요?
            </div>
            
            <div class="cmhp-desc text">
                <p>지금 운영 중인 홈페이지, 우리 회사의 목적에 맞게 작동하고 있나요?</p>
                <p>많은 기업들이 여전히 디자인 중심의 소개형 홈페이지에 머물러 있습니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cmhp-intro__images">
            <div class="cmhp-intro__person parallax" data-depth="0.9" data-direction="left">
                <div class="person__img">
                    <div class="person__img-inner"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="person__txt">
                    <div class="speech-bubble" data-direction="left">단순한 정보제공?</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cmhp-intro__person parallax" data-depth="0.7" data-direction="right">
                <div class="person__img">
                    <div class="person__img-inner"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="person__txt">
                    <div class="speech-bubble" data-direction="right">회사 소개?</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    import "../../../public/js/commercialHp/commercialHp1.js";
</script>
